		{"id":"g_trend","type":"group","x":1620,"y":920,"width":500,"height":300,"color":"4","label":"前沿技术趋势"},
		{"id":"n_daily_plan","type":"text","text":"## 学期中 (每天2-3h)\n\n- 1h 视频教程/看书\n- 1h 代码练习/做项目\n- 0.5h 刷LeetCode\n- 周末集中做项目\n- 坚持写学习笔记","x":1340,"y":1300,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_daily_holiday","type":"text","text":"## 假期冲刺 (每天6-8h)\n\n- 上午: 系统学习新知识\n- 下午: 项目实战开发\n- 晚上: 复盘+算法训练\n- 每个假期完成1个项目\n- 寒假: 基础+进阶\n- 暑假: 框架+微服务+项目","x":1640,"y":1300,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_trend_ai","type":"text","text":"## AI + Java\n\n- Spring AI 框架\n- LangChain4j\n- 向量数据库集成\n- RAG应用开发","x":1640,"y":1100,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_trend_big","type":"text","text":"## 大数据 (了解)\n\n- Hadoop / Spark\n- Flink流处理\n- Hive数据仓库\n- Java是大数据基础语言","x":1880,"y":1100,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_books_video","type":"text","text":"## 视频教程\n\n- **黑马程序员** (B站免费)\n- 尚硅谷系列\n- 韩顺平Java\n- 动力节点\n- 官方文档必读","x":20,"y":1300,"width":180,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_books_book","type":"text","text":"## 经典书籍\n\n- 《Java核心技术》\n- 《Effective Java》\n- 《Java并发编程实战》\n- 《深入理解JVM》\n- 《Spring实战》\n- 《设计模式之禅》","x":220,"y":1300,"width":180,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_books_site","type":"text","text":"## 网站与社区\n\n- 菜鸟教程 (入门)\n- 掘金/思否 (文章)\n- Stack Overflow\n- GitHub Trending\n- 牛客网 (面试)\n- LeetCode (算法)","x":420,"y":1300,"width":180,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_interview_soft","type":"text","text":"## 软技能\n\n- 简历撰写 (STAR法则)\n- 项目经验包装\n- 开源贡献 (GitHub)\n- 技术博客写作","x":1340,"y":1100,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_career_dir","type":"text","text":"## 主要方向\n\n| 方向 | 技术栈 | 特点 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 后端开发 | Spring Cloud全家桶 | 需求最大 |\n| Android | Kotlin/Java | 客户端开发 |\n| 大数据 | Hadoop/Spark/Flink | 数据驱动 |\n| 游戏服务端 | Netty/游戏逻辑 | 薪资高 |","x":680,"y":1300,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_career_tips","type":"text","text":"## 求职建议\n\n- **大二暑假**: 开始投实习\n- **大三**: 冲刺秋招/春招\n- 重点打磨2-3个精品项目\n- GitHub活跃度很重要\n- 技术博客加分项\n- 参加开源项目 / 编程竞赛\n- 学校实验室/导师项目经验","x":980,"y":1300,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_trend_new","type":"text","text":"## Java新方向\n\n- **Virtual Threads** (Project Loom)\n- **GraalVM** 原生镜像\n- **Quarkus** 云原生框架\n- **Micronaut** 轻量框架\n- **Kotlin** (Android首选)","x":1640,"y":960,"width":220,"height":120,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_trend_cloud","type":"text","text":"## 云原生与DevOps\n\n- Kubernetes (K8s)\n- Serverless / FaaS\n- Service Mesh\n- 可观测性 (监控/日志/追踪)\n- Infrastructure as Code","x":1880,"y":960,"width":220,"height":120,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_interview_core","type":"text","text":"## Java核心面试题\n\n- JVM内存模型\n- GC垃圾回收\n- HashMap底层原理\n- 并发与锁\n- Spring IOC/AOP\n- MyBatis缓存机制","x":1100,"y":960,"width":220,"height":120,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_interview_algo","type":"text","text":"## 算法面试 (必备)\n\n- LeetCode Hot 100\n- 排序/二分/双指针\n- 链表/二叉树/回溯\n- 动态规划基础\n- 每天1-2题保持手感\n- 牛客网面经","x":1340,"y":960,"width":220,"height":120,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_interview_jvm","type":"text","text":"## JVM深入\n\n- 类加载机制\n- 内存区域 (堆/栈/方法区)\n- 垃圾回收算法\n- JVM调优参数\n- Arthas诊断工具","x":1100,"y":1100,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_web_basic","type":"text","text":"## Web基础\n\n- HTTP协议原理\n- HTML/CSS/JS基础\n- Servlet/JSP (了解原理)\n- Tomcat 服务器\n- 请求/响应/会话\n- Cookie/Session","x":560,"y":580,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_web_spring","type":"text","text":"## Spring全家桶 (核心)\n\n- **Spring Boot 3** (必学)\n  - 自动配置原理\n  - Starter依赖管理\n- **Spring MVC**\n  - RESTful API\n  - 参数绑定\n- **Spring Security** (认证授权)","x":800,"y":580,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_web_mybatis","type":"text","text":"## ORM框架\n\n- MyBatis / MyBatis-Plus\n- JPA / Hibernate\n- SQL映射和动态SQL","x":560,"y":760,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_web_api","type":"text","text":"## API开发\n\n- RESTful设计规范\n- Swagger/Knife4j文档\n- 统一响应封装\n- 全局异常处理","x":800,"y":760,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_proj_small","type":"text","text":"## 入门项目\n\n1. 图书管理系统 (CRUD练手)\n2. 学生成绩管理系统\n3. 个人博客系统 (Spring Boot)\n4. 在线问卷调查系统","x":560,"y":960,"width":220,"height":120,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_proj_mid","type":"text","text":"## 进阶项目\n\n5. 电商系统 (前后端分离)\n6. 短信验证码登录系统\n7. 文件上传下载服务\n8. 在线聊天室 (WebSocket)","x":800,"y":960,"width":220,"height":120,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_proj_big","type":"text","text":"## 毕设/竞赛项目\n\n9. 分布式秒杀系统\n10. 校园外卖平台\n11. 在线考试系统\n12. 智能推荐系统","x":560,"y":1100,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_proj_port","type":"text","text":"## 项目规范\n\n- Git分支管理\n- API文档编写\n- 单元测试 (JUnit5)\n- 代码评审习惯","x":800,"y":1100,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_db_mysql","type":"text","text":"## MySQL基础\n\n- SQL语法 (CRUD)\n- 表设计和约束\n- 索引原理\n- 事务 (ACID)\n- 联表查询\n- 子查询/视图","x":20,"y":580,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_db_jdbc","type":"text","text":"## JDBC\n\n- 驱动连接\n- Statement/PreparedStatement\n- ResultSet处理\n- 事务管理\n- 连接池 (Druid/HikariCP)\n- DAO模式","x":260,"y":580,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_db_nosql","type":"text","text":"## NoSQL (了解)\n\n- Redis 缓存\n- MongoDB 文档库\n- 使用场景对比","x":20,"y":760,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_db_tool","type":"text","text":"## 数据库工具\n\n- Navicat / DataGrip\n- DBeaver (免费)\n- SQL优化技巧","x":260,"y":760,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_basic_syntax","type":"text","text":"## 语法基础\n\n- 变量与数据类型\n- 运算符和表达式\n- 流程控制\n  - if/else/switch\n  - for/while/do-while\n- 数组 (一维/二维)\n- 方法定义和调用","x":560,"y":160,"width":220,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_basic_api","type":"text","text":"## 常用API\n\n- String / StringBuilder\n- Math / Random / Date\n- 包装类 (Integer等)","x":560,"y":380,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_basic_oop","type":"text","text":"## 面向对象 (核心)\n\n- 类和对象\n- 封装/继承/多态\n- 抽象类和接口\n- 构造方法\n- static 和 final\n- this/super 关键字\n- toString/equals 重写","x":800,"y":160,"width":220,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_basic_ex","type":"text","text":"## 异常处理\n\n- try/catch/finally\n- throws/throw\n- 自定义异常","x":800,"y":380,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_deploy_linux","type":"text","text":"## Linux基础\n\n- 常用命令 (cd/ls/grep等)\n- 文件权限管理\n- Vim编辑器\n- Shell脚本基础\n- 进程/服务管理\n- CentOS/Ubuntu","x":20,"y":960,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"n_title","type":"text","text":"# Java学习路线图 (2025)\n面向学生的现代化Java全栈学习路径","x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_env_jdk","type":"text","text":"## JDK版本\n\n- **推荐 JDK 21** (LTS)\n- JDK 17 也可\n- OpenJDK 或 Oracle JDK\n- 了解 GraalVM 原生编译","x":20,"y":160,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_env_ide","type":"text","text":"## IDE选择\n\n- **IntelliJ IDEA** (首选)\n  - 社区版免费\n  - 学生免费旗舰版\n- VS Code (轻量)\n- Eclipse (备选)","x":260,"y":160,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_env_build","type":"text","text":"## 构建工具\n\n- Maven (传统稳定)\n- Gradle (现代主流)\n- 推荐先学 Maven","x":20,"y":340,"width":220,"height":120,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_env_git","type":"text","text":"## 版本控制\n\n- Git 基础命令\n- GitHub / Gitee\n- 学会用 .gitignore","x":260,"y":340,"width":220,"height":120,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_deploy_docker","type":"text","text":"## Docker容器化\n\n- 镜像/容器概念\n- Dockerfile编写\n- Docker Compose\n- 常用镜像拉取\n- 容器网络和卷\n- Docker Hub","x":260,"y":960,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"n_deploy_cicd","type":"text","text":"## CI/CD\n- Jenkins / GitHub Actions","x":20,"y":1140,"width":220,"height":40,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"n_deploy_cloud","type":"text","text":"## 云服务\n- 阿里云/腾讯云学生优惠","x":260,"y":1140,"width":220,"height":40,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"n_why_java","type":"text","text":"## 为什么学Java？\n就业面广 · 生态成熟 · 薪资稳定 · 大厂首选 · Android开发 · 大数据生态","x":650,"y":0,"width":500,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_fe_three","type":"text","text":"## 三件套基础\n\n- **HTML5** 语义化标签\n- **CSS3** Flex/Grid布局\n- **JavaScript ES6+**\n  - 变量/函数/对象\n  - DOM操作\n  - fetch API\n- 不需要精通，够用即可","x":1640,"y":580,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_fe_vue","type":"text","text":"## Vue 3 (推荐)\n\n- 组件化开发\n- 响应式数据\n- Vue Router\n- Pinia 状态管理\n- Axios 请求库\n- Element Plus UI","x":1880,"y":580,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_fe_ts","type":"text","text":"## TypeScript (加分)\n\n- 类型系统\n- 接口/泛型\n- 与Java思维相通","x":1640,"y":760,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_fe_react","type":"text","text":"## React (备选)\n\n- JSX语法\n- Hooks\n- 大厂偏好React\n- 学一个框架即可","x":1880,"y":760,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_summary","type":"text","text":"**总时长**: 约8-12个月（学生节奏） | **核心路线**: Java基础 → 进阶 → 现代特性 → 数据库 → Spring Boot → 微服务 → 前端 → 部署 | **关键理念**: 基础扎实 + 项目驱动 + 持续刷题 + 保持好奇心 = 成为合格的Java开发者","x":0,"y":1580,"width":1940,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_mod_stream","type":"text","text":"## Stream API (重点)\n\n- filter / map / reduce\n- flatMap / collect\n- Optional 类\n- 并行流 parallelStream\n- Collectors 工具类\n- 链式编程思维","x":1640,"y":160,"width":220,"height":200,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_mod_features","type":"text","text":"## Java 17-21 新特性\n\n- var 局部变量类型推断\n- Record 类 (不可变数据类)\n- Sealed 类 (密封类)\n- Text Block (多行字符串)\n- Pattern Matching\n- Switch 表达式\n- Virtual Threads (21)","x":1880,"y":160,"width":220,"height":200,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_mod_func","type":"text","text":"## 函数式编程\n\n- FunctionalInterface\n- 方法引用\n- Consumer/Supplier\n- Predicate/Function","x":1640,"y":380,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_mod_design","type":"text","text":"## 设计模式入门\n\n- 单例模式\n- 工厂模式\n- 观察者模式\n- 策略模式","x":1880,"y":380,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"n_micro_svc","type":"text","text":"## 微服务架构\n\n- Spring Cloud\n- Nacos (注册/配置中心)\n- Gateway (网关路由)\n- OpenFeign (远程调用)\n- Sentinel (限流熔断)\n- 链路追踪 (SkyWalking)","x":1100,"y":580,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_micro_mq","type":"text","text":"## 消息队列\n\n- RabbitMQ (入门首选)\n- Kafka (高吞吐)\n- RocketMQ (阿里系)\n- 异步解耦思想\n- 延迟队列/死信队列\n- 消息可靠性保证","x":1340,"y":580,"width":220,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_micro_redis","type":"text","text":"## Redis深入\n\n- 数据结构详解\n- 缓存穿透/击穿/雪崩\n- 分布式锁\n- Spring Data Redis","x":1100,"y":760,"width":220,"height":90,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_micro_search","type":"text","text":"## 搜索引擎\n\n- Elasticsearch\n- Kibana可视化\n- 分词与索引\n- 全文检索实践","x":1340,"y":760,"width":220,"height":90,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_adv_collections","type":"text","text":"## 集合框架 (重点)\n\n- List (ArrayList/LinkedList)\n- Set (HashSet/TreeSet)\n- Map (HashMap/TreeMap)\n- Queue/Deque\n- Collections工具类\n- Iterator 迭代器","x":1100,"y":160,"width":220,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"n_adv_generic","type":"text","text":"## 泛型与高级特性\n\n- 泛型类/方法/接口\n- 泛型通配符\n- 枚举类型\n- 注解 (Annotation)\n- 反射 (Reflection)\n- Lambda 表达式","x":1340,"y":160,"width":220,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"n_adv_io","type":"text","text":"## IO与文件\n\n- 字节流/字符流\n- BufferedReader/Writer\n- NIO (Path/Files)\n- 序列化","x":1100,"y":380,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"n_adv_thread","type":"text","text":"## 多线程基础\n\n- Thread / Runnable\n- synchronized\n- 线程池 (Executor)\n- CompletableFuture","x":1340,"y":380,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"2"}
	],
